item.title: RealityScape - Need Players - Unique - Just started
item.dc:creator: @crash_bad crash bad
item.description:
@crash_bad wrote:

This is absolutely a great server, I’ve been playing it for nearly a month. Honestly guys, the only thing I’ve ever wanted from the server that Reality cannot directly influence which is the players. Please, join and stick around for a while, you’ll essentially be completing the server.

If you’re looking for a good 317, old school server but you still appreciate some challenge in training skills and managing to keep your gear while PK’ing, Reality is definitely the place for you.
